Description (en): Building apps and end-use cases for humanoids

DEUS is the native utility and governance token of the XMAQUINA ecosystem, offering holders early exposure to Physical AI. It provides access to a diversified treasury of private robotics companies, tokenized machine assets, and the rise of humanoids. Staking DEUS unlocks voting rights over ecosystem initiatives and treasury allocations. As the machine economy expands, value generated across the portfolio and ecosystem accrues to the DAO treasury and is collectively governed to create sustainable, long-term value for builders, contributors, and token holders.
Description (zh): DEUS 是 XMAQUINA 生态系统的原生实用和治理代币，为持有者提供早期接触物理 AI 的机会。它提供对多样化私人机器人公司、代币化机器资产和人类化身的多元化储备的访问。质押 DEUS 解锁对生态系统倡议和储备分配的投票权。随着机器经济的发展，整个投资组合和生态系统产生的价值将积累到 DAO 储备中，并由集体治理以创造可持续的长期价值，为建设者、贡献者和代币持有者创造价值。

Description (en): OVER is a leading Physical AI platform building the world's largest 3D map. Leveraging a Decentralized Physical Infrastructure Network (DePIN) framework, OVER incentivizes a global community of mappers with OVR Tokens to scan high-traffic locations using common smartphones and 360-degree cameras. With over 150,000 locations mapped and 60 million+ images, OVER possesses the most extensive 3D Map dataset globally. This proprietary data powers diverse Physical AI applications: from training cutting-edge Vision Foundation Models to enabling precise Visual Positioning Systems and fostering AI-powered Extended Reality (XR) publishing and browsing.
Description (zh): OVER 是领先的物理人工智能（Physical AI）平台，致力于构建全球最大的 3D 地图。通过采用去中心化物理基础设施网络（DePIN）框架，OVER 激励全球的制图者社区，使用普通智能手机和 360 度相机扫描人流密集区域，并通过 OVR 代币进行奖励。目前，OVER 已映射超过 150,000 个地点，拥有超过 6,000 万张图像，是全球最大的 3D 地图数据集。该专有数据为多种物理人工智能应用提供支持：从训练先进的视觉基础模型（Vision Foundation Models）、实现高精度视觉定位系统（Visual Positioning Systems），到推动基于人工智能的扩展现实（XR）内容发布与浏览。
Tag: DePIN, DePAI, Robotics, Physical AI, Data

Description (en):
Silencio is building the world’s ears for AI and robotics.
 Silencio powers voice AI, robotics, AR/VR, and spatial intelligence with ethically sourced, audio data at scale. With over 1.1 million users and >41 billion datapoints contributed, we are building the foundational layer for machine hearing. The market for real-world audio intelligence is projected to exceed $100 billion by 2030, fueled by virtual assistants, healthcare, robotics, and support systems. As demand for field data surges, Silencio is positioned as the go-to audio layer, capable of capturing any language, in any corner of the world.
 We transform everyday devices into a decentralized network of real-world audio sensors. Unlike traditional data models that extract information without consent, every datapoint is contributed voluntarily. Participation is always opt-in, anonymized, and rewarded, ensuring privacy and transparency.

YOM is the first peer-to-peer decentralized cloud gaming network (DePIN), enabling near-zero-cost pixel streaming across gaming, architectural visualization, animation, immersive content, and the metaverse. By eliminating reliance on centralized cloud providers, YOM delivers cost-efficient, high-quality gaming instantly to any device, enhancing accessibility and scalability for developers and players alike. Powered by $YOM, the network incentivizes node operators to provide GPU resources, enabling seamless, high-fidelity experiences on any device—including mobile, MacBooks, tablets, XR headsets, and even platforms like Telegram, apps, and websites. Node operators can stake $YOM to increase their yield, while a built-in burn mechanism continuously reduces supply, making $YOM deflationary as network adoption grows.
Description (zh): YOM 是首个点对点去中心化云游戏网络（DePIN），实现了在游戏、建筑可视化、动画、沉浸式内容和元宇宙等领域近乎零成本的像素流式传输。通过消除对中心化云提供商的依赖，YOM 提供高效、低成本的高质量游戏体验，使开发者和玩家能够即刻在任何设备上畅玩。$YOM 作为网络的核心动力，激励节点运营商提供 GPU 资源，实现无缝、高清的游戏体验，支持移动设备、MacBooks、平板、XR 头显，甚至 Telegram、应用程序和网站等平台。节点运营商可以质押 $YOM 以提高收益，同时内置销毁机制随着网络使用增长而减少供应，使 $YOM 具有通缩特性。
